info.author: WuBook Srl
info.description: ZaK is a property management system for hotel and bed and breakfast, natively connected with a booking and reservations system to be implemented on hotel sistes. It's also connected with a channel manager supporting the most important online travel agencies as expedia.
info.keywords: property management system, open source, hotel, bed and breakfast, booking engine, online booking, channel manager
info.name: ZaK
info.platform: any, ZaK requires only the twisted framework
info.summary: ZaK is a property management system for hotel and bed and breakfast
